prodNameC: 羅氏免疫分析抗促甲狀腺素受體抗體檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
PreciControl：
PC Thyro1: 1 bottle, for 2.0 mL of control serum
Anti-TSHR antibody (human) approx. 4 IU/L in a human serum matrix.
PC Thyro2: 1 bottle, for 2.0 mL of control serum
Anti-TSHR antibody (human) approx. 16 IU/L in a human serum matrix.

Reagent：
Reagent rackpack
M  Streptavidin-coated microparticles, 1 bottle, 6.5 mL: 
Streptavidin-coated microparticles 0.72 mg/mL; preservative. 
R1  Buffer solution 1 bottle, 7 mL: 
Phosphate buffer 20 mmol/L, pH 7.4; stabilizers; preservative.
R2  Anti-TSHR~Ru(bpy)2+3,1 bottle, 7 mL:
Monoclonal anti-TSHR antibody M22 (human) labeled with ruthenium complex approx. 0.3 mg/L; phosphate buffer 20 mmol/L, pH 7.4; stabilizers, preservative.
Calibrators
Cal1 Anti-TSHR calibrator 1, 1 bottles (lyophilized) for 2.0 mL :
Anti-TSHR antibody (human) approx. 1.0 IU/L in a human serum matrix.
Cal2 Anti-TSHR calibrator 2, 1 bottles (lyophilized) for 2.0 mL :
Anti-TSHR antibody (human) approx. 25 IU/L in a human serum matrix.

Pretreatment rackpack
PT1 Pretreatment buffer solution, 1 bottle, 4 mL:
Phosphate buffer 20 mmol/L, pH 7.4; stabilizers; preservative.
PT2 Empty bottle for pretreatment reagent (PTR)
reconstituted with pretreatment buffer (PTB)
PTR Pretreatment reagent, pTSHR-anti-pTSHR-Ab~biotin complex
1 bottle for 4 mL of PTB:
Phosphate buffer 40 mmol/L, pH 7.2; stabilizers.
PTB Pretreatment buffer 1 bottle, 5 mL:
Reconstitution medium for PTR; phosphate buffer
10 mmol/L, pH 7.2; stabilizer.
applicantName: 台灣羅氏醫療診斷設備股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區民權東路3段2號10樓
efficacy: 使用一個人類甲狀腺刺激的單株抗體，對人類血漿中抗促甲狀腺素受體的自體抗體進行體外定量檢測之免疫分析法。
